product.longDescription: Our largest jalapeño offering, Jedi's fruits avg. 4–4 1/2" and are slow to check (show small cracks in skin). The large plant produces over a long harvest window, especially in regions with a long growing season. Our jalapeño variety with the highest potential yield. High resistance to bacterial leaf spot races 1-3. Avg. 65,000 seeds/lb. Packet: 25 seeds.
